{"tid":131691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣先施舖4.68億易手 內地投資者勁蝕4.64億元","createTime":"2017-02-23T08:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T12:42:33.000Z","uid":54373,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c889990850bc09fbcda2378079a45fa71effa8","tid":131691,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"近期積購舖投資的冠華鏡廠許氏家族，剛斥資4.68億元購入銅鑼灣現先施舖位，原業主內地投資者劉軍勁蝕億元離場。<br />\n<br />\n冠華鏡廠購入波斯富街108至120號寶榮大樓地下AA號舖、1及2樓，約2.2萬方呎，成交價4.68億元，呎價2.13萬元。舖位現由先施百貨承租，月租150萬元，回報3.8厘。<br />\n<br />\n劉軍在2012年中，斥巨資11.42億元購入寶榮大樓地下至2樓共23,932方呎樓面，為當年矚目成交。不過，舖位丟空超過一年才由先施承租大部份樓面，而地下AB號舖更長期租不出。<br />\n<br />\n直至2014年底，劉軍劈價五成，以2.1億元出售地下AB號舖予宏安（1222），連同上址，共套現約6.78億元，賬面勁蝕4.64億元，持貨5年合共勁蝕40.6%。"},{"pid":"7a76e80e5220f3637456ceb1d3c722400dccb51b","tid":131691,"uid":76112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"d11fc6d18a0a95e23b7ad4ea6e52277a02cedc66","tid":131691,"uid":50984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9750429c766b5bea0b19c28e6c0e7977d6a5f29b","tid":131691,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e57cccf230356ec463623656ec444643d3fe53","tid":131691,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/170102_66ab6dab4a5c46e34c831c411665c643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F170102_66ab6dab4